[
    {
        "text": "Can employers make vaccines mandatory?",
        "startTime": 1336,
        "endTime": 3719,
        "slowStartTime": 2154,
        "slowEndTime": 5803
    },
    {
        "text": "You know, what's possible will really depend on what country you're in.",
        "startTime": 4711,
        "endTime": 7937,
        "slowStartTime": 7217,
        "slowEndTime": 12131
    },
    {
        "text": "Some countries like Canada, it's certainly quite hard.",
        "startTime": 8287,
        "endTime": 11308,
        "slowStartTime": 12580,
        "slowEndTime": 17187
    },
    {
        "text": "In Britain, if you are hiring new staff, then, certainly, that does appear to be the case.",
        "startTime": 11766,
        "endTime": 17587,
        "slowStartTime": 17799,
        "slowEndTime": 26606
    },
    {
        "text": "I know that employers here do want to do this for existing staff...",
        "startTime": 18311,
        "endTime": 23834,
        "slowStartTime": 27617,
        "slowEndTime": 35976
    },
    {
        "text": "...and I think what we will see in Britain and in other countries...",
        "startTime": 24131,
        "endTime": 27697,
        "slowStartTime": 36346,
        "slowEndTime": 41771
    },
    {
        "text": "...is that this will get tested legally as employers bring this in.",
        "startTime": 27797,
        "endTime": 32361,
        "slowStartTime": 41845,
        "slowEndTime": 48766
    },
    {
        "text": "And in the United States,...",
        "startTime": 32597,
        "endTime": 34058,
        "slowStartTime": 49046,
        "slowEndTime": 51312
    },
    {
        "text": "...state governments and private employers can definitely mandate vaccines.",
        "startTime": 34163,
        "endTime": 37842,
        "slowStartTime": 51394,
        "slowEndTime": 56988
    },
    {
        "text": "There are three exceptions that tend to come into play.",
        "startTime": 38173,
        "endTime": 42054,
        "slowStartTime": 57409,
        "slowEndTime": 63306
    },
    {
        "text": "There's personal beliefs, religion, as well as medical exceptions.",
        "startTime": 42316,
        "endTime": 47428,
        "slowStartTime": 63624,
        "slowEndTime": 71367
    },
    {
        "text": "And in some states, like California and New York,...",
        "startTime": 47863,
        "endTime": 51312,
        "slowStartTime": 71945,
        "slowEndTime": 77193
    },
    {
        "text": "...they don't even actually allow for a religious exemption...",
        "startTime": 51662,
        "endTime": 54653,
        "slowStartTime": 77643,
        "slowEndTime": 82205
    },
    {
        "text": "...or a personal belief exemption.",
        "startTime": 54755,
        "endTime": 56125,
        "slowStartTime": 82282,
        "slowEndTime": 84413
    },
    {
        "text": "So, it's actually quite surprising when you dig in.",
        "startTime": 56470,
        "endTime": 59640,
        "slowStartTime": 84855,
        "slowEndTime": 89685
    },
    {
        "text": "Do you think governments will ever make COVID vaccines mandatory?",
        "startTime": 60380,
        "endTime": 64107,
        "slowStartTime": 90720,
        "slowEndTime": 96385
    },
    {
        "text": "Well, we know that they have in Saudi Arabia.",
        "startTime": 64491,
        "endTime": 67112,
        "slowStartTime": 96886,
        "slowEndTime": 100893
    },
    {
        "text": "We know that the Moscow government...",
        "startTime": 67237,
        "endTime": 69090,
        "slowStartTime": 101006,
        "slowEndTime": 103860
    },
    {
        "text": "...has rolled out a mandatory vaccination program for service sector workers.",
        "startTime": 69209,
        "endTime": 74641,
        "slowStartTime": 103964,
        "slowEndTime": 112186
    },
    {
        "text": "So, I think it's clear that some governments will do this.",
        "startTime": 74748,
        "endTime": 78003,
        "slowStartTime": 112272,
        "slowEndTime": 117229
    },
    {
        "text": "It is not constitutional for the federal government...",
        "startTime": 78160,
        "endTime": 81670,
        "slowStartTime": 117390,
        "slowEndTime": 122730
    },
    {
        "text": "...to require all US citizens to get a vaccine.",
        "startTime": 81745,
        "endTime": 84487,
        "slowStartTime": 122768,
        "slowEndTime": 126955
